---
export const prerender = true;
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Use - GymDō"
  description="GymDō terms of use."
>
  <section class="section bg-black">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-black text-white mb-4">Terms of Use</h1>
        <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm mb-12">Last updated: March 2026</p>

        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">1. Acceptance</h2>
            <p class="text-zinc-400">By using GymDō, you agree to these terms. If you do not agree, please do not use the service.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">2. Service</h2>
            <p class="text-zinc-400">GymDō provides gym management software for BJJ academies. We reserve the right to modify or discontinue the service with reasonable notice.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">3. Payments</h2>
            <p class="text-zinc-400">Subscriptions are billed monthly. Cancellation takes effect at the end of the current billing period. The first 30 days are free with no credit card required. We offer a 30-day money back guarantee on your first paid month.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">4. Your data</h2>
            <p class="text-zinc-400">You retain ownership of your data. On cancellation, you may request an export of your data within 30 days.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">5. Limitation of liability</h2>
            <p class="text-zinc-400">GymDō is provided as-is. We are not liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from use of the service.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">6. Governing law</h2>
            <p class="text-zinc-400">These terms are governed by the laws of Queensland, Australia.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">7. Contact</h2>
            <p class="text-zinc-400">Email <a href="mailto:josh@cmdsoftware.com.au" class="text-red-400 hover:text-red-300">josh@cmdsoftware.com.au</a> with any questions.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
